Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,THE DEMONIC GUARD OF HEAVEN AND EARTH
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:02:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you became my teacher of darkness\Nto raise me to be your perfect body!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! You're too late in realizing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I found you\Nafter you had left Aban, I had an idea.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how strong it is,\Nthis body is still King Ban's.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not mine.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I find a replacement, it might\Nnot be compatible with my dark power.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if I were to raise one from scratch{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and train it to use the greatest\Ndark power, it would be the perfect spare.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should the time come\Nto return King Ban's body,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it would be the perfect weapon for me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A weapon?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I was to you was a weapon.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. You're my weapon. My tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There were times when I considered killing\Nyou, but I'm glad I kept you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, you served me well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found it! Your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, now you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike that girl, the erasure of your soul\Nwon't be temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This soul will be disintegrated\Nand you will become a living puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, at last, we will become one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My spirit and your body will create\Na warrior that will rival Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider it an honor! You get to be\Na successor to King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Aura of Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, you focused Aura of Light\Ninto your own soul?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't move well anyways,\Nso this was all I could do.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But you couldn't have gathered\Nthis much power in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not unless you knew I would possess you!\NHow did you know?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You were certain to choose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hyunckel!\N-Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Myst?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He died...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So the never-ending struggle between\Nmaster and student of darkness has ended.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He should be happy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He got to die in the perfect body\Nthat he raised over the years.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I... to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why won't you attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that supposed to be\Nthe ultimate body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake, Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Myst?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's gone from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You banished it, didn't you, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-By driving it from my body.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, ahem, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I couldn't have done it\Nwithout everyone's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'd rather not let her know\Nabout your dark connection with Myst.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can tell just how important\NMaam is to you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm well aware.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp and Grand Master were killed by Myst.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're awake, Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell? We're healing.\NIt's healing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I disguised myself as Kilban,\NI rescued them from the Medoroa spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I left their unconscious bodies behind\Nand put on my disguise,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but with all the excitement,\NI never got a chance to explain.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they just woke up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like they meant to worry you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Maam, you're not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam? Maam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you being all prickly for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Are you thinking,\N"I should be the one to heal Popp!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We understand, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear. And after I healed him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure she still doesn't have\Nsome residual evil in her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. Those two are always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's always Popp's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-Be that as it may, Captain...\N-Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Medicinal Herbs\Ndon't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you cast any Heal-type magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem! I cannot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's go help Master Dai!\NAre you ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... I was so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always so thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a little violent\Nfor trying to hide your relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Get up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hoimi spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cast it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only him, but anyone with major damage\Nshould either stay here or head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No. After all this, there's no going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to steal Hyunckel's line,\Nbut I want to see this battle through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it costs you your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm scared to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as Mystban's body,\NBan's power was near perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Up there, he now has the elder body's\NMagic Power and intellect as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:10:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how terrifying\Nthe bodies were apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'd honestly rather not\Nface them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I could ask you the same, Larhart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't do a thing against Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing there's someone even stronger,\Nwhy do you still go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A foolish question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I can't do anything, it doesn't\Nmatter so long as Master Dai wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To die for that cause is my duty\Nas leader of the Dragon Masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I am but a shield for Master Dai,\Nthen so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That alone makes going worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well there you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're the same as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No one here believes that\Nthey can actually face the Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But we've made up our minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Win or lose, we're still going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... Dai's up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The more shields there are, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,To Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:31.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4}GRAND CROSS{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:36.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}GIGA STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It should take about five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Five... four... three...\Ntwo... one... zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:11:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm healing! My body's healing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be fully healed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that Leona's Behoma spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Behoma spell cast on you while\Nyou were unaffected by Hoimi-type magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it has finally taken effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would revert soon,\Nand I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When fighting beyond your limits\Nwith Aura similar to Dark Aura,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes such backlashes\Nto the body can occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Weak beings can even die from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It can vary,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can estimate when someone will\Nbe restored from their eyes and skin tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you wait for that to happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So he could fight with me at full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite perceptive, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while\Nsince I've used this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Crushing an enemy not at their best\Nwould be utterly boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're going to fight, I'd prefer it be\Nafter you were fully healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't insult us!\NAre you trying to show off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Such threats won't work on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong with me? I can't speak.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All he did was glare at me\Nand it's like my body's frozen!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to threaten\Nor show off, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I genuinely look forward to fighting Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Secret Spell of Frozen Time is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:14:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the next full solar eclipse\Nin a few centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck in this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've taken a few centuries\Nof my immortal time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't pay the price,\Nthen I'll have been robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You are obligated to amuse me\Nas best as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's pure evil!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of understand what he means.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, don't be stupid! Don't listen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you're in that form,\Nyou're stronger than before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Much, much more so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Being that strong in this world\Nis just boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I enjoy fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I kind of understand how that feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like me, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pretend otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Descended from warriors,\Nyou have the blood of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can try to hide it,\Nbut your true nature reveals itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Child of a Dragon who was foolishly\Ndrawn to humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall tear off that mask you hide behind\Nand make you experience hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, I'm still me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm everyone's Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:16:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As I've already said, I haven't fought\Nin this body in thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hold back,\Nso it might be over rather quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll forgive me if it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandiose talk before a battle\Nisn't my style!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's Giga Strash!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the most powerful attack I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I do enjoy that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're bold and rational.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,While you can appear reckless,\Nyou use the most logical attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To see how strong he is...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To know our difference in strength,\Nusing my strongest attack is the best way.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And this attack takes time to prepare,\Nso it's difficult to use in a close match.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a head-on approach!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I should show you\Na skill worthy of your attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive that you instantly understood\Nthe danger of this stance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the Demonic Guard\Nof Heaven and Earth - Tenchimato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenchimato?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To my eyes it just looks like\Nhe's taken a simple stance.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there's no way it can be that simple.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just look at how Dai is sweating!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And now let our greatest skills clash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of us will fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you back down now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I should tell you that\Nyour judgement is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Giga Strash is indeed\Nthe best attack to use...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,win or lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Giga Strash is the strongest attack\Nthat I have!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,my only...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,option!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not dodging!\NIs he going to try to take it?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Giga Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Phoenix Wing!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Calamity End!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&H00FF00&}Kaiser Phoenix!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to explain while my hand heals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Dai fall in an instant?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the secret to\NTenchimato
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ten" is the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Chi" is defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And "Mato" is reminiscent of\Nthe use of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can attack, defend, and use magic\Nin a single instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This impenetrable stance is\Nthe Tenchimato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As an old man, two of the three\Nis all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But this young body allows me\Nto fight in such a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:20:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,With this ultimate skill,\Nno matter how lethal an attack one uses,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course he couldn't win.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Giga Strash is a mix of magic\Nand attack that uses the Magic Sword.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But his opponent can add defense to that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyone who charges into that stance\Nwill have their attack nullified,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and be simultaneously torn apart\Nby his attack and magic.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see even the strong-willed princess\Nis at a loss for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away... from Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be shielded by your Dragonic Aura,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's nothing\NCalamity End can't cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No blade in the world can match\Na strike from the side of my palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you've realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That wound is in the exact same place\Nthat you cut me before.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you shall slowly feel my wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've come up\Nwith an entertaining idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You must serve beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:17.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:28.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:36.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:45.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:02.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even Dai's Giga Strash didn't work against\Nthe Demonic Guard of Heaven and Earth.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.20,0:23:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ban tries to make Leona his own\Nto make Dai feel despair.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meeting fierce resistance, he shows signs\Nof quiet anger for the first time.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.13,0:23:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As Dai falls into peril again,\NPopp and the others arrive.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.64,0:23:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Eye Jewel"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
